All tasks completed successfully. Here's a summary:

**Compilation Errors Found:** 5 errors in `NisAppConfig.java` related to Flyway API changes (constructor and setter methods no longer exist in Flyway 9.x)

**Transformation Created:** `/workspace/javaparser-base-template/src/main/java/github/chains/Main.java`
- Uses JavaParser AST manipulation to transform Flyway usage
- Converts old API (`new Flyway()` + setters) to new builder API (`Flyway.configure()...load()`)
- Skips `setClassLoader` which doesn't exist in Flyway 9.x

**Fix Applied:** The `flyway()` method in `NisAppConfig.java` was transformed from:
```java
final org.flywaydb.core.Flyway flyway = new Flyway();
flyway.setDataSource(this.dataSource());
flyway.setClassLoader(NisAppConfig.class.getClassLoader());
flyway.setLocations(prop.getProperty("flyway.locations"));
flyway.setValidateOnMigrate(Boolean.valueOf(prop.getProperty("flyway.validate")));
return flyway;
```

To:
```java
return Flyway.configure().dataSource(this.dataSource()).locations(prop.getProperty("flyway.locations")).validateOnMigrate(Boolean.valueOf(prop.getProperty("flyway.validate"))).load();
```

**Verification:** `mvn compile` now succeeds for all 5 modules in the nem project.
